		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="408" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">渊火伸手从天落下大火球，掷向玩家，造成<span color="#ff9999">66.6%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深渊咏者%B7渊火.assets/Image_14.png')" x="1391" y="138">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ad4218" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#ad4218">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">渊火召唤5个小火球，依次朝玩家发射，每个火球都造成<span color="#ff9999">26.6%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="408" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">渊火汇聚火元素力量，蓄力产生爆炸，造成<span color="#ff9999">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="437" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">当渊火的生命值<span color="#ffbfbf">低于20%</span><span>时，踉跄并释放大范围的爆炸，造成</span><span color="#ff9999">133.3%</span><span>伤害，并附属</span><span textDecoration="underline" color="#ff9999">赤烬加护</span><span>，使用</span><span color="#7fbfff">水</span><span>破盾最有效，盾破后渊火立即死亡。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="991" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">渊火持续操作黯火炉心，其不断在场上产生3批一组的火喷，火喷的效果同样会造成<span color="#ff663f">「烙火」</span><span>效果。施放10组火喷后停止施放并摧毁黯火炉心。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="408" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">渊火从空中降下炎心之陨，坠地爆炸，造成<span color="#ff9999">66.6%</span><span>伤害，并留下</span><span textDecoration="underline">黯火炉心</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深渊咏者%B7渊火.assets/Image_15.png')" x="719" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深渊咏者%B7渊火.assets/Image_16.png')" x="719" y="361">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深渊咏者%B7渊火.assets/Image_17.png')" x="1392" y="586">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深渊咏者%B7渊火.assets/Image_18.png')" x="718" y="906">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深渊咏者%B7渊火.assets/Image_19.png')" x="1391" y="361">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="66" y="1008" width="440" height="78" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">赤烬加护：<span color="#ff9999">72火</span><span>盾，击破后渊火立即死亡，可伤害转化。该状态下，抗打断0，免疫风场力。 黯火炉心：</span><span color="#ff9999">12火</span><span>盾，击破后反噬渊火12盾量，并暂时打断技能施放。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
