		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深渊咏者%B7渊火.assets/Image_31.png')" x="596" y="939" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深渊咏者%B7渊火.assets/Image_32.png')" x="576" y="918" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="926" width="425" height="178" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="32" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffb299">固有天赋：蹈火<br/><span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">依据火咏者的血量、核心状态的不同，<br/>其分为3个战斗阶段：<br/></span><span fontSize="24" color="#ff794c">阶段1：</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">还没开盾；<br/></span><span fontSize="24" color="#ff794c">阶段2：</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">开盾后，拥有</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ff794c">「黯火炉心」</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">；<br/></span><span fontSize="24" color="#ff794c">阶段3：</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">开盾后，无</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ff794c">「黯火炉心」</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">存在。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="439" height="200" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">渊火旋转法器，在地上召唤3个火喷，每个造成<span color="#ff9999">26.6%</span><span>伤害，</span><span color="#ff794c">阶段2后</span><span>施放2次。火喷命中角色后，若未被护盾有效庇护，则会被</span><span color="#ff663f">「渊火烙印」</span><span>标记：<br/></span><span color="#99ff99">扣除全队角色生命值的15%+当前渊火的13.3%攻击力</span><span>，每个角色独立计算，</span><span color="#ff9999">后台生命值低于15%不再扣除，不致死</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
